bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-aYNvzOdB0uFNcME0KMqnUw">Rã thị thư biệt - 野巿書別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%ADch/Ti%C3%AAu-t%E1%BB%B1-th%E1%BA%A7n-chung/poem-UoAFzjcVqu27V-qQYHAeMA">Tiêu tự thần chung - 蕭寺晨鐘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%ADch/author-GLzqIGvVnoBURna-hgD_jw">Mạc Thiên Tích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C6%AFng-th%E1%BB%8B-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Ki4p0VkTv_lw5-py8ZVBJA">Tống Ưng thị kỳ 2 - 送應氏其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-D0kSTyyLojSiroomgDKkWw">Tự thán kỳ 2 - 自嘆其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/V%C4%83n-gi%C3%A1-c%C3%B4-thanh/poem-2je7WvNkMwRcKN81ty_Afg">Văn giá cô thanh - 聞鷓鴣聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
